<html>
  <head>
    <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.gstatic.com'>
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:wght@400;600&display=swap' rel='stylesheet'>
    <style type='text/css'>
      .ExternalClass,
      .ExternalClass div,
      .ExternalClass font,
      .ExternalClass p,
      .ExternalClass span,
      .ExternalClass td,
      img {
        line-height: 100%;
      }
      #outlook a {
        padding: 0;
      }
      .ExternalClass,
      .ReadMsgBody {
        width: 100%;
      }
      a,
      blockquote,
      body,
      li,
      p,
      table,
      td {
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      }
      table,
      td {
        mso-table-lspace: 0;
        mso-table-rspace: 0;
      }
      img {
        -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
        border: 0;
        height: auto;
        outline: 0;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      #bodyCell,
      #bodyTable,
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Prompt', Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      #bodyCell {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      #bodyTable {
        width: 600px;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
        #bodyTable,
        body {
          width: 100% !important;
        }
        a,
        blockquote,
        body,
        li,
        p,
        table,
        td {
          -webkit-text-size-adjust: none !important;
        }
        body {
          min-width: 100% !important;
        }
        #bodyTable {
          max-width: 600px !important;
        }
        #signIn {
          max-width: 280px !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <center>
      <div
        style='
          -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
          -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
          mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
          mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          font-family: 'Prompt', Arial, sans-serif;
          border-collapse: collapse !important;
          height: 100% !important;
        '
        height='100%'
      >
        <div style='padding-top: 55px;'>
          <img
            src='https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/html-bag.s3.getbud.co/branding/bud-logotype.png'
            alt='Logotipo do Bud'
            width='72px'
            height='auto'
            style='
              -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
              border: 0;
              height: auto;
              line-height: 100%;
              outline: none;
              text-decoration: none;
            '
          />
        </div>

        <div style='max-width: 600px;'>

          <div style='padding: 44px 0;'>
            <h1 style='font-weight: 700;'>Você recebeu um novo comentário no seu resultado-chave! 🎤</h1>

            <p style='
              font-size: 18px;
              color: #525F7F;
            '>
              {{ownerFirstName}}, seus resultados-chave estão dando o que falar. Confira o comentário que você acabou de receber:
            </p>
          </div>

          <div style='
            border-top: 1px solid #DDE5EE;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #DDE5EE;
            padding: 29px 0;
          '>
            <table cellspacing='18px'>
              <tr>
                <td style='vertical-align: top'>
                  <div
                    style='
                      max-width: 50px;
                      max-height: 50px;
                      border: 1px solid transparent;
                      border-radius: 9999px;
                      overflow: hidden;
                    '
                  >
                    <img
                      width='50px'
                      height='50px'
                      src='{{authorPictureURL}}' />
                  </div>
                </td>

                <td>
                  <div style='padding-bottom: 14px;'>
                    <h2
                      style='
                        font-weight: 700;
                        font-size: 16px;
                        color: #525F7F;
                        margin: 0;
                      '
                    >
                      {{authorFullName}}
                    </h2>

                    <p
                      style='
                        font-size: 14px;
                        color: #8193AB;
                        margin: 0;
                      '
                    >
                      comentou no seu resultado-chave:
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <table>
                    <tr>
                      <td
                        style='
                          width: 2px;
                          height: 100%;
                          border: 1px solid transparent;
                          border-radius: 9999px;
                          background-color: {{keyResultConfidenceTagColor}};
                          padding: 0;
                        '
                      />

                      <td>
                        <h3
                          style='
                            color: #525F7F;
                            font-size: 16px;
                            font-weight: 700;
                            line-height: 20px;
                            margin: 0;
                            padding: 9px 0 9px 14px;
                          '
                        >
                          {{keyResultTitle}}
                        </h3>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <p
                    style='
                      font-size: 14px;
                      line-height: 18px;
                      color: #8193AB;
                    '
                  >
                    “{{keyResultComment}}"
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>

          <div style='
            padding: 44px 0;
            width: 400px;
          '>
            <p
              style='
                font-size: 18px;
                color: #525F7F;
              '
            >
              Para responder, acesse o Bud e navegue até a barra lateral desse resultado-chave:
            </p>

            <div style='padding: 29px 0 0 0;'>
              <a href='https://app.getbud.co/meus-resultados-chave'>
                <button
                  style='
                    border: 1px solid transparent;
                    border-radius: 6px;
                    background-color: #6F6EFF;
                    color: #FFFFFF;
                    font-size: 14px;
                    font-weight: 700;
                    padding: 21px 0;
                    width: 300px;
                    cursor: pointer;
                  '
                >
                  Abrir o Bud
                </button>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
                
        <div
          style='
            margin-top: 55px;
            background-color: #F6F8FE;
            padding: 55px 0;
          '
        >
          <div
            display='inline-block'
            style='padding-bottom: 21px;'
          >
            <a
              href='https://www.linkedin.com/company/getbud/'
              style='
                margin-right: 11px;
                text-decoration: none;
              '
            >
              <img
                src='https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/html-bag.s3.getbud.co/icons/linkedin-outline.png'
                alt='Ícone do LinkedIn'
                style='
                  -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
                  border: 0;height: auto;
                  line-height: 100%;
                  outline: none;
                  text-decoration: none;
                '
              />
            </a>
            <a href='https://getbud.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portals'>
              <img
                src='https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/html-bag.s3.getbud.co/icons/support-outline.png'
                alt='Ícone do helpdesk'
                style='
                  -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
                  border: 0;
                  height: auto;
                  line-height: 100%;
                  outline: none;
                  text-decoration: none;
                '
              />
            </a>
          </div>
          <p
            style='
              text-align: center;
              color: #7E8CA4;
              -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
              -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
              font-size: 13px;
            '
          >
            Se você não fez essa solicitação, entre em contato conosco
            respondendo a este e-mail.
          </p>

          <p
            style='
              text-align: center;
              color: #7E8CA4;
              -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
              -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
              font-size: 13px;
              padding-top:21px;
            '
          >
            Copyright © 2020, bud - Todos os direitos reservados.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </center>
  </body>
</html>
